OL,5,G0325 Build Your Own Home
OL,6,     FThe residents of beautiful Clare
OL,7,     FIsland off Co. Mayo are frustrated
OL,8,     Fwith the tourist facilities. Over
OL,9,     Fa series of workshops, they
OL,10,     Fcollaborate to boost the island's
OL,11,     Funique offering.
